<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='347461' id='t-347461'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:03
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='352058' id='t-352058'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
